Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.14,2:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fn이순신 Regular\blur6\shad1\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&\t(0,500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(500,1000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(1000,1500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(1500,2000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(2000,2500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(2500,3000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(3000,3500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(3500,4000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)}사방의 문은 닫고,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.22,2:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fn이순신 Regular\blur6\shad1\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&\t(0,500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(500,1000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(1000,1500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(1500,2000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(2000,2500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(2500,3000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(3000,3500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(3500,4000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)}왕관에서 나와,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.91,2:00:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fn이순신 Regular\blur6\shad1\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&\t(0,500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(500,1000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(1000,1500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(1500,2000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(2000,2500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(2500,3000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)\t(3000,3500,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HE89C80&)\t(3500,4000,\3c&HFFDC5A&\4c&HBD4016&)}왕국에 이르는 세 갈래 길은 순환하라!
